org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.components.FCM

Interface UseInstanceConfigurator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UseInstanceConfiguratorImpl

    public interface UseInstanceConfigurator
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Use Instance Configurator'. Use a dedicated component that that is responsible for configuring component instances. The concept is primarily intented for container extensions. For instance, a container extension might provide reflection data about a component. In this case, the instance configuration would create the value specifications using data available in the model

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Class
    • Configurator
    See Also:
